('Jesus can sit with you in the ache without demanding a performance.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('Your heart is worth tending gently.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('God can make beauty grow in soil that grief watered.', NULL, 'saying', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('You are not alone when the night feels long.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'I will never leave thee, nor forsake thee.', 'Hebrews 13:5 KJV', 'approved'),
('The Lord understands groans that never become sentences.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('You can let prayer be small today.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('Grace does not ask you to pretend you are fine.', NULL, 'saying', 'My grace is sufficient for thee: for my strength is made perfect in weakness.', '2 Corinthians 12:9 KJV', 'approved'),
('God can rebuild trust slowly and tenderly.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Trust in the LORD with all thine heart; and lean not unto thine own understanding.', 'Proverbs 3:5 KJV', 'approved'),
('You are deeply loved in the middle of your process.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('The Lord can steady what trauma shook.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('God is not distant from your tears.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'And God shall wipe away all tears from their eyes.', 'Revelation 21:4 KJV', 'approved'),
('You can bring the younger, hurting parts of you to Jesus.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is nigh unto them that are of a broken heart.', 'Psalm 34:18 KJV', 'approved'),
('Lord, help me feel Your nearness where I feel afraid.', NULL, 'prayer', 'Let us therefore come boldly unto the throne of grace, that we may obtain mercy.', 'Hebrews 4:16 KJV', 'approved'),
('God''s grace can find you even when you feel hard to find.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'My grace is sufficient for thee: for my strength is made perfect in weakness.', '2 Corinthians 12:9 KJV', 'approved'),
