('Your story can still carry light.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('God is faithful in the breath between now and next.', NULL, 'saying', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('You can ask God for help before you feel brave.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('The Lord can cover the places where shame has been loud.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('Mercy meets you before you get yourself together.', NULL, 'saying', 'It is of the LORD''s mercies that we are not consumed, because his compassions fail not.', 'Lamentations 3:22 KJV', 'approved'),
