('Lord, remind me that I am not alone in this room.', NULL, 'prayer', 'Let us therefore come boldly unto the throne of grace, that we may obtain mercy.', 'Hebrews 4:16 KJV', 'approved'),
('Jesus is near enough for this moment.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Draw nigh to God, and he will draw nigh to you.', 'James 4:8 KJV', 'approved'),
