('The Lord''s kindness can reach behind the wall you built to survive.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('You can be honest, tired, and loved at the same time.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Come unto me, all ye that labour and are heavy laden, and I will give you rest.', 'Matthew 11:28 KJV', 'approved'),
('Grace can hold what you cannot explain.', NULL, 'saying', 'My grace is sufficient for thee: for my strength is made perfect in weakness.', '2 Corinthians 12:9 KJV', 'approved'),
