('The Lord can lead you beside still waters again.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('You are allowed to receive comfort without guilt.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Blessed are they that mourn: for they shall be comforted.', 'Matthew 5:4 KJV', 'approved'),
('Christ is not far from the bruised heart.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('Lord, give me courage without taking away my tenderness.', NULL, 'prayer', 'Let us therefore come boldly unto the throne of grace, that we may obtain mercy.', 'Hebrews 4:16 KJV', 'approved'),
('God can renew strength without demanding that you hide your weakness.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'God is our refuge and strength, a very present help in trouble.', 'Psalm 46:1 KJV', 'approved'),
('Your worth was never dependent on being unhurt.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is nigh unto them that are of a broken heart.', 'Psalm 34:18 KJV', 'approved'),
('The Lord can turn fear into trust one tiny surrender at a time.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Fear thou not; for I am with thee: be not dismayed; for I am thy God.', 'Isaiah 41:10 KJV', 'approved'),
('Even here, God is still good and still near.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'Draw nigh to God, and he will draw nigh to you.', 'James 4:8 KJV', 'approved'),
('You can let the Word of God speak gently over your nervous system.', NULL, 'encouragement', 'The LORD is good, a strong hold in the day of trouble; and he knoweth them that trust in him.', 'Nahum 1:7 KJV', 'approved'),
('The same Jesus who calmed the sea can calm the storm inside you.', NULL, 'saying', 'Peace I leave with you, my peace I give unto you: not as the world giveth, give I unto you.', 'John 14:27 KJV', 'approved');
